---
title: Quick Korean Ssamjang Beef & Veggies with Rapid Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: This sizzling Korean-style beef is a joy unparalleled. Simplicity is the winner here, with a ssamjang stir-fry sauce on the beef strips being the crowning glory on this quick and easy weeknight winner.
